---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<section class="scroll-mt-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50 to-white dark:from-slate-900 dark:to-slate-800" id="context">
	<div class="px-4 py-16 mx-auto max-w-6xl lg:px-8 lg:py-20">
		<div class="mb-10 md:mx-auto sm:text-center md:mb-12 max-w-3xl">
			<p class="text-base text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-200 font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase">时代背景</p>
			<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tighter tracking-tighter mb-4 font-heading">
				AI时代的教育变革
			</h2>
			<p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto sm:text-center text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
				人工智能正在重新定义教育的核心价值，这不是边际优化，而是范式革新
			</p>
		</div>

		<!-- 三大冲击 -->
		<div class="mb-12">
			<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-8">AI带来的全方位冲击</h3>
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
				<div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
					<div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 mb-4 rounded-full bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900">
						<Icon name="tabler:brain" class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600 dark:text-red-400" />
					</div>
					<h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">知识层面</h4>
					<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">
						AI可以瞬间检索和整合全人类知识库，记忆和复述不再是人类的优势
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
					<div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 mb-4 rounded-full bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-900">
						<Icon name="tabler:robot" class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400" />
					</div>
					<h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">技能层面</h4>
					<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">
						机器在规则明确、流程固定的任务上已全面超越人类
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
					<div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 mb-4 rounded-full bg-yellow-100 dark:bg-yellow-900">
						<Icon name="tabler:chart-dots" class="w-6 h-6 text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400" />
					</div>
					<h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">认知层面</h4>
					<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">
						AI在数据分析、模式识别、逻辑推理等方面展现出惊人能力
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- 教育转型的核心 -->
		<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-secondary-500 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12 text-white">
			<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">教育必须重新定义自己的价值</h3>
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
					未来教育的核心不再是传授固定的知识和技能，而是培养那些AI难以替代的<strong>人类独特能力</strong>：
				</p>
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-6">
					<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
						<Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" />
						<span>想象力和创造力</span>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
						<Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" />
						<span>批判性思维和价值判断</span>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
						<Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" />
						<span>情感智慧和社会协作</span>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
						<Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" />
						<span>审美能力和艺术表达</span>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
						<Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" />
						<span>伦理思考和道德选择</span>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
						<Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" />
						<span>终身学习和适应能力</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- 五大转变 -->
		<div class="space-y-6">
			<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-8">教育的根本性转变</h3>

			<div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-lg p-6 border-l-4 border-blue-500">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-2">
					<Icon name="tabler:arrow-right" class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-500" />
					<h4 class="text-lg font-bold">从应试导向到能力导向</h4>
				</div>
				<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 ml-10">
					不再以考试分数为唯一标准，而是关注学生的综合素养和创新能力
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-lg p-6 border-l-4 border-purple-500">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-2">
					<Icon name="tabler:arrow-right" class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-500" />
					<h4 class="text-lg font-bold">从知识灌输到思维培养</h4>
				</div>
				<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 ml-10">
					不再机械传授知识点，而是培养学生的学习能力和思维品质
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-lg p-6 border-l-4 border-green-500">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-2">
					<Icon name="tabler:arrow-right" class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500" />
					<h4 class="text-lg font-bold">从标准化到个性化</h4>
				</div>
				<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 ml-10">
					不再用统一标准衡量所有学生，而是发现和培养每个学生的独特潜能
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-lg p-6 border-l-4 border-orange-500">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-2">
					<Icon name="tabler:arrow-right" class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-500" />
					<h4 class="text-lg font-bold">从教师中心到学生中心</h4>
				</div>
				<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 ml-10">
					不再是教师单向传授，而是学生主动探索和建构
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-lg p-6 border-l-4 border-red-500">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-2">
					<Icon name="tabler:arrow-right" class="w-6 h-6 text-red-500" />
					<h4 class="text-lg font-bold">从封闭系统到开放生态</h4>
				</div>
				<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 ml-10">
					不再局限于课堂和教材，而是链接真实世界和社会资源
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
